					<h1>The layout</h1>
					<p>The layout was finalized on February 28, 2016; It was made in HTML, CSS and Javascript with jQuery. I <a href="https://br.linkedin.com/in/victor-carlos-671537b4"> Victor Carlos </a>, developer of social network, introduced the same for my uncle who is the IT area. He pointed the design mistakes and I was in doubt: I do or not do? I decided to do, slicing the entire site and moving to PHP.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="wrap">
					<a name="Development" ></a>
					<h1>The Development</h1>
					<p>I started to slice up the entire project by placing QueryString and the database was already drawn on paper. After all this work, created with the bank, started to create classes, models and controllers, along with the connection driver. It was decided that the project would be the MVC model.</p>
					<p>Basic tests were done by creating fictitious accounts and developing features.</p>
				</div>
				
